1
00:00:02,938 --> 00:00:05,989
Michael, could you help me, please?
迈克  请问你可以帮我一下吗

2
00:00:06,021 --> 00:00:08,485
Sure. What is it?
当然可以  怎么了

3
00:00:08,538 --> 00:00:14,085
We are going to have a soccer game against Class Five on Saturday.
我们周六将和五班有一场足球比赛

4
00:00:14,106 --> 00:00:18,810
But one of my teammates fell ill. Will you join us?
但我们有一个队员生病了  你能加入我们吗

5
00:00:18,864 --> 00:00:25,210
I'd be glad to. But I am not very good at it. Would you mind teaching me?
我很愿意加入  但我不太擅长  你能教教我吗

6
00:00:25,253 --> 00:00:27,760
Not at all. You can do it!
没问题  你可以的

7
00:00:27,802 --> 00:00:29,760
Let's go and practice.
我们去练习一下吧

8
00:00:30,208 --> 00:00:34,597
Kangkang and Michael are practicing on the playground.
康康和迈克在操场上练习足球

9
00:00:34,880 --> 00:00:41,621
Michael, I kick the ball to you. And you pass me the ball like this.
迈克  我把球踢给你  你这样传球给我

10
00:00:41,722 --> 00:00:44,085
Sorry, I missed it.
抱歉  我错过了球

11
00:00:44,176 --> 00:00:49,178
Never mind. Keep trying. I'll kick you the ball again.
没事  继续尝试  我会再把球踢给你

12
00:00:49,253 --> 00:00:50,549
OK.
好的

